Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, when\Ndoes the noon train
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.61,0:00:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,from the Crystal\NEmpire arrive?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.74,0:00:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, noon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.68,0:00:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. Right. Sorry, I'm\Njust a little excited
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,because my friend\NSunburst is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my oldest friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.19,0:00:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, we've known each\Nother practically forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.92,0:00:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We have tons in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.23,0:00:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We both love magic and games\Nand jokes. Everything, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.60,0:00:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, there\Nisn't a pony in all of Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I have more in\Ncommon with.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunburst: Starlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.99,0:01:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunburst!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.46,0:01:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.63,0:01:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.56,0:01:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking forward to\Nthis visit for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.24,0:01:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.94,0:01:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you staying?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.81,0:01:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Er.. just a... little\Nreading for the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Same old Sunburst.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.32,0:01:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.55,0:01:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be so great\Nspending time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.45,0:01:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like old times.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.55,0:01:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You and me doing the stuff\Nwe like: games, magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.12,0:01:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Antiquing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.46,0:01:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Antiquing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.36,0:01:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I like antiquing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.83,0:01:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.80,0:01:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Historical knickknacks,\Nancient relics.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! You are SO lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.77,0:01:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponyville is antique central!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It is..?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.64,0:01:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How have we never\Ntalked about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.68,0:01:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going antiquing\Nand you are gonna love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Let's drop your stuff\Noff at the castle first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.78,0:02:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! Only.. heh.. we may need\Nto make a few trips.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.33,0:02:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knew I'd be\Nthe one showing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.03,0:02:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you the cool sights\Nof Ponyville?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little surprised, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.57,0:02:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, what a difference between\Nthe hoof-molded bricks
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.51,0:02:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and the extruded ones, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh huh. Ha ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh! Check out all\Nthese chandeliers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes the crystals\Nhave magical properties.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.76,0:03:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. That's cool.\NHow do you--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight: Sunburst!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad\Nyou're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,In the antique store?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight's really been\Nlooking forward to your visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I'm glad you're\Nin the antique store too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm usually the only one...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Who doesn't\Nlike antiquing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.84,0:03:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh... right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,An ancient map of Equestria\Nmade by the Mighty Helm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Without the help of unicorn\Nmagic or pegasus flight,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the earth ponies\Nof the Mighty Helm
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,were able to map the\Nentire coast of Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.13,0:03:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Coooool..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to pretend\Nto like all this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No. I\Ndo like it. Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if you\Nlike it, I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, we've almost\Nlooked at everything.. right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight: Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.51,0:04:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You have got to see this\NSaddle Arabian vanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.91,0:04:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This shop looked a lot\Nsmaller from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see this\NPalominian letter opener?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! That goes well with this\Nancient Phoenix feather quill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We could write\Nto each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,PEN PALS!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Um.. I really like this\Nold-timey barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, the stuff I\Nbought is inside the barrel,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't wait\Nto see what it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you don't know\Nwhat you bought?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.56,0:05:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-mm! It's a blind buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes shops get too busy\Nto go through everything
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.94,0:05:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,so they load up a box\Nor barrel and sell it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,without knowing\Nwhat's inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Buying one is sort of\Nlike a treasure hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I found a first edition\NHistory of Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,in the original Olde Ponish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"{\i1} Hliet foresettan pliht."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an Olde Ponish saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"Reward prefers risk."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. It... loses something\Nin the translation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm. [giggle]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. Why don't we look\Nthrough this stuff later?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.67,0:06:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. What do you want\Nto do, Starlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know if you're\Ngoing to remember this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON PIT!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember\Nthat game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You two used\Nto play it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. Pretty much any time we\Nweren't working on magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe\Nyou found a copy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunburst would get so excited\Nwhenever his dragon got trapped
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,he'd knock the whole board over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh.. well, it's an exciting game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have a little more\Ncontrol over my horn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Somepony's dragon's\Ngonna get trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.26,0:07:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't seem so\Nexciting to m--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.33,0:07:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,AAAHAHHAHAHH!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. I guess it is adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you're enjoying\Nyour visit so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.61,0:07:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, first antiquing and then\Nspending time with Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She's.. pretty great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? I mean, I know\Nshe's a Princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but I never thought she'd be so\Nfun to just hang out with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she is the\NPrincess of Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckle] Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So. Tomorrow\NI thought--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I'm just surprised\Nat how well we get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have much in\Ncommon with most ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.70,0:07:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are pretty similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know many ponies who\Nare fluent in Olde Ponish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably have more in\Ncommon with Twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:08:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,than any pony in Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.68,0:08:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I better\Nget some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[yawn] Ponyville might be small,\Nbut there's a lot to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should ask Twilight\Nwhat she recommends we see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! Goodnight, Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[door opens]\NKnock, knock!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.04,0:08:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Hi, Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it morning already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a bit early,\Nbut like you said,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a lot to\Nsee in Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, right. OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.09,0:08:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. Plus, I couldn't really sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I just kept thinking about all\Nthe stuff we have in common
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and how much fun\Nwe'll have today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. Is Twilight up yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Actually, I'm pretty sure she's\Nbusy with Princess stuff today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. [yawn]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.07,0:09:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've got a full day of stuff\Nplanned, just you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Um. Would you mind turning\Naround, or preferably...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving the room so\NI could get changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Right! Ha ha,\Nsorry, ah ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,One, genuine, Sweet\NApple Acres apple tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we used to drink so\Nmuch apple juice as foals?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.. I don't remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I mean, it\Nwas all we drank.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh.. here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Try an apple. I bet that'll jog your memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.71,0:09:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Ow..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.25,0:09:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Trixie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I often seek the privacy of\Nthe orchard to practice
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,new feats of amazement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.93,0:09:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And, also I fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.06,0:09:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Well, Sunburst and I\Nwere just catching up, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.77,0:09:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] I don't suppose the two\Nof you want to see
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,a never-before-witnessed\Nmagical marvel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] Why not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold, visiting friend\Nfrom Starlight's past
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and be amazed by the\NGreat and Powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.02,0:10:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and current best friend\Nof Starlight, TRIXIE!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I give you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,THE UNICORN ESCAPE!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,One more...twist...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and... [grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The great and\Npowerful Trixie
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,requires a little\Nassistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a special link,\Nbut I could never
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,hold the chain up long\Nenough to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.37,0:11:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if I could\Ndo magic like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have a whole slew of new\Ntricks at my disposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I always liked close up magic\Nbecause I knew I could do it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,if I just practiced enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight, why\Ndidn't you tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.26,0:12:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,how much Sunburst\Nand I had in common?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I know Trixie's "magic"\Nis, you know, fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but the Mirror Pool\Nis actual magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.81,0:12:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! This place\Nis pure ponylore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.94,0:12:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. I mean, it's supposed\Nto be all dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.08,0:12:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I shouldn't have\Nbroken the seal to get in,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.32,0:12:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but you wanted to see the\Nsights of Ponyville, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Pinkie Pie just dove in\Nand made copies of herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.46,0:12:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If we made copies of ourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,we could get a year's worth of\Nhanging out over in one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh.. not that we would.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh. I hope it's not a\Nleft over Pinkie Pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Maud: Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Maud? How did\Nyou get in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:12:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This cavern's actually\Nconnected to mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.. what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Tapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Maud isn't\Nsuper chatty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you and I could sit\Naround and talk all day,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but she looks pretty busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you taking some\Nkind of core sample?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm uncovering this section\Nof strata for closer study.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You might want to step back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm studying this\Narea's metamorphic--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,--foliation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this gneiss,\Nphyllite, or slate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. The pressure above\Nmust be pretty uniform
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to get the planar fabric\Nto be this consistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You know about geology?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I dabble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, by the\Nspeleothems in this cave,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.06,0:13:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I kinda figured there\Nwas another way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the\Ncalcite deposits.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Sunburst?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing stage magic with Trixie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Studying new rocks with Maud?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here so I guess you\Ntwo aren't off translating
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,some ancient Olde Ponish text.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would Sunburst\Nbe doing any of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he came to\NPonyville to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so too, but it\Nhasn't worked out that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,When we were foals,\Nwe had more in common
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,than any two ponies\Nin Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But now it seems like\Nhe's got more in common
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,with my friends than\Nhe does with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Everypony changes,\Nbut that doesn't mean
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,there aren't still\Nthings you both like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You both love magic, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. You're\Nreally good at it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.90,0:15:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and Sunburst practically knows\Nevery spell that ever was.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh. I try.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.77,0:15:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Maud and I found some\Nfascinating sedimentary stratum,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but when I turned to\Nshow you, you were gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.32,0:15:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Maud does have a way of making\Nrocks really interesting,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but I wanted to work on\Nsomething a little more "us."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little\Nsomething I made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.30,0:15:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! You made up this\Nspell? Just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But wait, there's more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can play Dragon Pit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.60,0:16:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like we used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I thought we\Ncould go with Maud and--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, nothing was better\Nthan just you and me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,playing this game when\Nwe were foals, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you what to be red or blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.65,0:16:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to play\Nthe game at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. I was trying to have\Nfun doing the ONE thing
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we still\Nhad in common,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but I guess we don't even\Nhave that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight and I have known each\Nother since we were foals,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.69,0:17:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but that doesn't mean we\Nhave to be foals to hang out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.09,0:17:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. Starlight does have a\Ntendency to over-do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it is surprising how\Nwell I get along with
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.16,0:17:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,all of her friends, but she and\NI still have tons in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you just need to remind\Nher what those things are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly what I'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Right after I think of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously you and I hit it\Noff. I am quite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.22,0:17:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And we share a love\Nfor prestidigitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And Starlight and I share\Na lot of things too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need to\Nthink of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.73,0:17:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What else do you\Nguys have in common?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.03,0:17:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we've both made\Nnot-so-great choices in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're self-conscious about\Neverypony judging us
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,even though we've\Nboth changed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.31,0:17:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and are trying hard\Nto be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... we don't really have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! I can think of\Nsomething you have in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're both poor\Npractice audiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight and I don't really\Nhave a lot in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Other than feeling\Ndifferent from most ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And comedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Comedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's more\Nthan I can think of
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that she and I\Nhave in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't really spend that much\Ntime talking about that, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mostly we're just comfortable\Naround each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] We used to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We did everything together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I'm wondering if we've\Nspent so much time apart
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.19,0:18:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that we don't connect\Nover anything anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and if we can't\Nconnect over anything
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,then maybe we're\Nnot even friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.26,0:18:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at least\Nit's not serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.83,0:18:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That.. was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:19:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] I appreciate you trying\Nto help, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems pretty clear that\NSunburst and I have grown apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.25,0:19:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But I feel like that only\Nhappens if you both let it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You still want to\Nbe friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I created a spell so we could\Nre-live playing a game
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.49,0:19:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in our childhood home...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Right....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just not sure Sunburst\Nwants to stay friends too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you might\Nbe surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,For the new\Nand improved
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon Pit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We had to take out a few\Nspaces to get it to fit
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but you hardly miss them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.05,0:19:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maud made the dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Pumice is the\Nlightest igneous rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the\Nbest choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.06,0:19:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And I added the special effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing like a little\Nwell-placed magic smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like somepony's dragon\Nis going to get trapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.27,0:20:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you didn't\Nwanna play this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.11,0:20:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't want to\Npretend to be a foal,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but I know you\Nwanted to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it'd be fun to\Nplay a version big enough
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,for full grown ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.51,0:20:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.62,0:20:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Fun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's\Nmissing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,AHHHGHHHHHH!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckle] Now it's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why I got\Nso worried about us
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,not having anything\Nin common.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I kind of think\Nit doesn't matter
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as we enjoy\Neach other's company.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.59,0:20:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Trixie: And that game was\Ncertainly enjoyable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What made it even better\Nwas getting to play it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,with all my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,See you soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hear if you find\Nanything interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.34,0:21:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,in that barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me, Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.01,0:21:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be the\Nfirst to know!
